{
  "slug": "predictive-restriction-and-temporal-thresholds",
  "type": "html",
  "title": "Evidence Threshold and First Events",
  "concept": "A system requiring observable evidence before intervention cannot prevent the event that generates that evidence — the first occurrence creates the data the threshold needs.",
  "interactiveId": "0bbe4afc-b06f-4574-aea4-8e7b5be08558",
  "sourcePieceId": "9eab8da6-7dac-4e9d-a56b-0d610035a1e2",
  "publishedAt": 1777342092065,
  "voiceScore": 90,
  "qualityFlag": "low",
  "content": {
    "type": "html",
    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n<title>Evidence Threshold and First Events</title>\n<style>\n  :root {\n    --bg: #faf7f1;\n    --fg: #1a1a1a;\n    --muted: #6b6b6b;\n    --line: #e5e0d6;\n    --gold: #c9a227;\n    --teal: #1a6b62;\n    --event-pending: #d9534f;\n    --event-occurred: #8b4513;\n    --prevented: #5cb85c;\n  }\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n  body {\n    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif;\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 20px;\n    color: var(--fg);\n    background: var(--bg);\n    line-height: 1.5;\n  }\n  h2 {\n    font-size: 1.05rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin: 0 0 4px;\n  }\n  p.subhead {\n    margin: 0 0 20px;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .control-row {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 12px;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n  }\n  button {\n    padding: 8px 16px;\n    border: 1px solid var(--line);\n    background: #fff;\n    color: var(--fg);\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n    font-weight: 500;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: all 120ms;\n  }\n  button:hover {\n    background: var(--line);\n  }\n  button:disabled {\n    opacity: 0.4;\n    cursor: not-allowed;\n  }\n  button:disabled:hover {\n    background: #fff;\n  }\n  .threshold-display {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 8px;\n    padding: 8px 14px;\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid var(--line);\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .threshold-display strong {\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: var(--gold);\n  }\n  .stage {\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid var(--line);\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    padding: 20px;\n    margin: 20px 0;\n  }\n  .evidence-counter {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 12px;\n    margin-bottom: 16px;\n    padding: 12px;\n    background: var(--bg);\n    border-radius: 4px;\n  }\n  .counter-label {\n    font-size: 0.85rem;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: 0.06em;\n  }\n  .counter-value {\n    font-size: 1.5rem;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\n    color: var(--teal);\n  }\n  .threshold-marker {\n    font-size: 0.85rem;\n    color: var(--gold);\n    font-weight: 600;\n  }\n  .event-queue {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 12px;\n    margin-bottom: 16px;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n  }\n  .event-box {\n    width: 80px;\n    height: 80px;\n    border: 2px solid var(--line);\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    font-size: 0.75rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    text-align: center;\n    transition: all 200ms ease-out;\n  }\n  .event-box.pending {\n    background: var(--event-pending);\n    color: #fff;\n    border-color: var(--event-pending);\n  }\n  .event-box.occurred {\n    background: var(--event-occurred);\n    color: #fff;\n    border-color: var(--event-occurred);\n    opacity: 0.6;\n  }\n  .event-box.prevented {\n    background: var(--prevented);\n    color: #fff;\n    border-color: var(--prevented);\n  }\n  .event-box.inactive {\n    background: #fff;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    border-color: var(--line);\n  }\n  .event-number {\n    font-size: 1.2rem;\n    margin-bottom: 4px;\n  }\n  .intervention-notice {\n    padding: 12px;\n    background: var(--prevented);\n    color: #fff;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n    opacity: 0;\n    transition: opacity 200ms;\n  }\n  .intervention-notice.active {\n    opacity: 1;\n  }\n  .summary {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;\n    gap: 8px 14px;\n    font-size: 0.85rem;\n    padding: 12px;\n    background: var(--bg);\n    border-radius: 4px;\n  }\n  .summary-label {\n    color: var(--muted);\n  }\n  .summary-value {\n    font-weight: 600;\n  }\n  p.caption {\n    margin: 14px 0 0;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-size: 0.875rem;\n  }\n  @media (max-width: 480px) {\n    .control-row {\n      flex-direction: column;\n    }\n    .event-queue {\n      justify-content: center;\n    }\n    .event-box {\n      width: 70px;\n      height: 70px;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<h2>Watch events occur one at a time</h2>\n<p class=\"subhead\">Each event generates one unit of evidence after it happens. Intervention becomes possible only when accumulated evidence meets the threshold.</p>\n\n<div class=\"control-row\">\n  <button id=\"nextBtn\">Next Event</button>\n  <button id=\"resetBtn\">Reset</button>\n  <div class=\"threshold-display\">\n    Threshold: <strong id=\"thresholdValue\">2</strong>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"stage\">\n  <div class=\"evidence-counter\">\n    <span class=\"counter-label\">Evidence:</span>\n    <span class=\"counter-value\" id=\"evidenceCount\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"threshold-marker\" id=\"thresholdStatus\">/ 2 needed</span>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"intervention-notice\" id=\"interventionNotice\">\n    Threshold met — intervention now possible\n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"event-queue\">\n    <div class=\"event-box pending\" data-event=\"1\">\n      <div class=\"event-number\">1</div>\n      <div>Pending</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"event-box inactive\" data-event=\"2\">\n      <div class=\"event-number\">2</div>\n      <div>Pending</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"event-box inactive\" data-event=\"3\">\n      <div class=\"event-number\">3</div>\n      <div>Pending</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"event-box inactive\" data-event=\"4\">\n      <div class=\"event-number\">4</div>\n      <div>Pending</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"event-box inactive\" data-event=\"5\">\n      <div class=\"event-number\">5</div>\n      <div>Pending</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"summary\">\n    <span class=\"summary-label\">Events occurred:</span>\n    <span class=\"summary-value\" id=\"occurredCount\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"summary-label\">Events prevented:</span>\n    <span class=\"summary-value\" id=\"preventedCount\">0</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"caption\" id=\"caption\">Event 1 has not occurred yet. No evidence exists. The threshold cannot be met.</p>\n\n<script>\n(function() {\n  var nextBtn = document.getElementById('nextBtn');\n  var resetBtn = document.getElementById('resetBtn');\n  var evidenceCount = document.getElementById('evidenceCount');\n  var thresholdStatus = document.getElementById('thresholdStatus');\n  var interventionNotice = document.getElementById('interventionNotice');\n  var caption = document.getElementById('caption');\n  var occurredCount = document.getElementById('occurredCount');\n  var preventedCount = document.getElementById('preventedCount');\n  var thresholdValue = document.getElementById('thresholdValue');\n  \n  var eventBoxes = document.querySelectorAll('.event-box');\n  \n  var threshold = 2;\n  var evidence = 0;\n  var currentEvent = 0;\n  var occurred = 0;\n  var prevented = 0;\n  var interventionActive = false;\n  \n  function updateDisplay() {\n    evidenceCount.textContent = evidence;\n    thresholdStatus.textContent = '/ ' + threshold + ' needed';\n    thresholdValue.textContent = threshold;\n    occurredCount.textContent = occurred;\n    preventedCount.textContent = prevented;\n    \n    if (evidence >= threshold && !interventionActive) {\n      interventionActive = true;\n      interventionNotice.classList.add('active');\n    }\n    \n    if (currentEvent >= 5) {\n      nextBtn.disabled = true;\n    } else {\n      nextBtn.disabled = false;\n    }\n    \n    updateCaption();\n  }\n  \n  function updateCaption() {\n    if (currentEvent === 0) {\n      caption.textContent = 'Event 1 has not occurred yet. No evidence exists. The threshold cannot be met.';\n    } else if (currentEvent === 1 && evidence < threshold) {\n      caption.textContent = 'Event 1 occurred and generated evidence. Total evidence: ' + evidence + '. Still below threshold (' + threshold + '). Event 1 could not have been prevented — it created the first evidence.';\n    } else if (currentEvent === 1 && evidence >= threshold) {\n      caption.textContent = 'Event 1 occurred and met the threshold immediately (threshold = 1). Even so, Event 1 could not be prevented — zero evidence existed before it happened.';\n    } else if (evidence < threshold) {\n      caption.textContent = 'Evidence: ' + evidence + ' / ' + threshold + '. Threshold not yet met. Events continue to occur, each adding to the evidence pool.';\n    } else if (interventionActive && prevented === 0) {\n      caption.textContent = 'Threshold met after Event ' + occurred + '. Intervention is now possible. Subsequent events can be prevented.';\n    } else {\n      caption.textContent = 'Intervention active. Events that would have occurred are now prevented. The first ' + occurred + ' event(s) generated the evidence that made intervention possible.';\n    }\n  }\n  \n  function processNextEvent() {\n    if (currentEvent >= 5) return;\n    \n    currentEvent++;\n    var box = eventBoxes[currentEvent - 1];\n    \n    if (interventionActive) {\n      box.classList.remove('pending', 'inactive');\n      box.classList.add('prevented');\n      box.querySelector('div:last-child').textContent = 'Prevented';\n      prevented++;\n    } else {\n      box.classList.remove('pending', 'inactive');\n      box.classList.add('occurred');\n      box.querySelector('div:last-child').textContent = 'Occurred';\n      evidence++;\n      occurred++;\n    }\n    \n    if (currentEvent < 5) {\n      eventBoxes[currentEvent].classList.remove('inactive');\n      eventBoxes[currentEvent].classList.add('pending');\n    }\n    \n    updateDisplay();\n  }\n  \n  function reset() {\n    evidence = 0;\n    currentEvent = 0;\n    occurred = 0;\n    prevented = 0;\n    interventionActive = false;\n    interventionNotice.classList.remove('active');\n    \n    for (var i = 0; i < eventBoxes.length; i++) {\n      eventBoxes[i].classList.remove('occurred', 'prevented', 'pending');\n      eventBoxes[i].classList.add('inactive');\n      eventBoxes[i].querySelector('div:last-child').textContent = 'Pending';\n    }\n    eventBoxes[0].classList.remove('inactive');\n    eventBoxes[0].classList.add('pending');\n    \n    updateDisplay();\n  }\n  \n  nextBtn.addEventListener('click', processNextEvent);\n  resetBtn.addEventListener('click', reset);\n  \n  updateDisplay();\n})();\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>"
  }
}
